er mysteries of life explained.</span><hr size=1> Daly, that is the most reasoned explaination I've seen so far in this thread other than &quot;!7 !5 4 /\/\4j!|&lt; d00|2,&quot; which can only draw my sarcasm, however, I would like to see proof (as in a screen shot rogue sensing a trap there).<br>
