Proud Member - <a href="http://www.ruconfused.com">Fortress of Honor</a></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub95.ezboard.com/uunfetered.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Unfetered</A> at: 3/27/02 1:48:58 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f7f7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub95.ezboard.com/uneochosen.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Neochosen</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Indifferent Poster</span><br> <font color=#778899>(3/26/02 8:36:12 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/finnoruukserverfrm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1456.topic&index=46>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.eqitems.com/tolstoy/aoshi.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: `</span><hr size=1> This does not hold true around walls Daly.  Take Ssra for example, right when you zone in there is a corner and then a door straight ahead.  If someone is fighting a mob just within the door and you are standing on the other side of the corner not only would you get the &quot;You cannot hit your target from here&quot; message, but you will also not be able to Hail the mob, even though if the wall was removed you would be able both melee and hail the mob.  Anyone who fights in Ssra would realize that mobs there have an extremely large melee range (bounding box), and that were the wall removed you would be within melee range of said mob, therefore, the problem is not that you must be standing on top of the mob to hit it (this holds true for other zones).  I can't count the number of times that when we were fighting in the old NToV safe spot I would run around the corner for a heal, yet still be well within what would normally be melee range, be facing the direction of the mob, and yet not be able to hit it nor hail it.<br>
<br>
(editted to make sure it was understood who I was addressing) <p><font face="Monotype Corsiva" size="4" color="#800000"><b><i>Tolstoy Wyldefyre</i></b></font><BR><font face="Bookman Old Style" size="2"><b>Wood Elf Warlord of Innoruuk</b></font><br><a href="http://legionsofdarkness.org"><font face="Bookman Old Style" size="2"><b>Legions of Darkness</b></font></a><br></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub95.ezboard.com/uneochosen.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Neochosen</A> at: 3/26/02 8:38:45 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f7f7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub95.ezboard.com/ugartegilsson.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gart Egilsson</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Indifferent Poster</span><br> <font color=#778899>(3/26/02 9:30:01 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/finnoruukserverfrm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1456.topic&index=47>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> <BR><img src=http://pantheon.yale.edu/~bdiebold/images/Gart1.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: `</span><hr size=1> <br>
